@Sam Alex:
I noticed that you installed "dpkg -i php5-mysql_5.1.6-1ubuntu2.4_i386.deb". You need to install the .deb with "mssql" in the name, not "mysql", if you need to get mssql functionality. It gets built into its own package, not bundled in with mysql. Hope this solves your problem!
-Robert

